01:12.800 --> 01:14.320
I'm really sorry.

01:14.320 --> 01:16.960
I hope it doesn't inconvenience you too much.

01:16.960 --> 01:19.200
It's just this thing came up and...

01:19.200 --> 01:21.920
Angela, you know what, I can't make it to our meeting either.

01:21.920 --> 01:24.960
