02:00.320 --> 02:03.200
The first word is reschedule.

02:03.200 --> 02:04.320
Reschedule.

02:04.320 --> 02:05.600
Reschedule.

02:05.600 --> 02:07.120
Reschedule.

02:07.120 --> 02:12.160
When you reschedule an appointment, you change it for another day or time.

02:12.160 --> 02:13.360
Exactly.

02:13.360 --> 02:16.720
Great, the second word that we have is inconvenience.

02:16.720 --> 02:18.320
In convenience.

02:18.320 --> 02:19.520
In convenience.

02:19.520 --> 02:21.360
In convenience.

02:21.360 --> 02:23.840
So to inconvenience, someone is to...

02:23.840 --> 02:27.760
To make things not convenient for that person.

02:27.760 --> 02:32.240
So to make things a little bit difficult to make things a little bit uncomfortable.

02:32.240 --> 02:33.520
A little comfortable.

02:33.520 --> 02:34.800
In convenience.

02:34.800 --> 02:36.960
And our third word is...

02:36.960 --> 02:37.920
Puzzpone.

02:37.920 --> 02:39.280
Puzzpone.

02:39.280 --> 02:40.480
Puzzpone.

02:40.480 --> 02:41.280
Puzzpone.

02:41.280 --> 02:43.760
We have some examples of the word postpone.

02:43.760 --> 02:46.640
That will help you to understand it's meaning a little bit better.

02:46.640 --> 02:47.200
Let's listen.

02:48.160 --> 02:49.040
Example one.

02:49.120 --> 02:54.080
