02:57.920 --> 02:58.720
Example two.

03:02.160 --> 03:05.520
I'm sorry Simon, but your vacation has been postponed until next month.

03:09.040 --> 03:10.080
Example three.

03:12.720 --> 03:14.880
Unfortunately, the flight will be postponed.

03:15.440 --> 03:20.560
Okay, so basically postpone is to delay.

03:20.560 --> 03:21.440
That's right.

03:21.440 --> 03:22.720
Make it at a later time.

03:22.720 --> 03:23.440
At a later time.

03:24.240 --> 03:26.080
