05:10.400 --> 05:11.040
Hi.

05:11.040 --> 05:12.160
Yeah, what's up?

05:12.160 --> 05:12.880
How's it going?

05:12.880 --> 05:13.760
What's going on?

05:13.760 --> 05:14.160
Right.

